text:
I had the pleasure of meeting Ms. Sindhu at Taiwan University of Science and Technology. She is the first female government school student from the Naan Mudhalvan Program doing her Masters Research program at Taiwan Tech, a significant achievement that underscores the program's success, which I personally observed during our interaction.

My sincere commendation goes to our esteemed Chief Minister, Mr. Stalin, and Deputy Chief Minister, Mr. Udhayanidhi, as well as the Ministry of School and Higher Education Department, for their instrumental role in making this dream a reality for government school students.
